subject: Automobile Racing
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
lead_paragraph: Joey Logano won his second straight race in the Chase for the Sprint Cup, spinning out Matt Kenseth with five laps remaining in Kansas City, Kan., and damaging Kenseth’s title hopes.
